  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE HBCU EQUITY FUND TO ELIMINATE DOCUMENTED EQUITY GAPS IN OPERATING FUNDING, ADDRESS DEFERRED MAINTENANCE AND CAPITAL NEEDS, AND SUPPORT ACADEMIC PROGRAMS, RESEARCH CAPACITY AND STUDENT SERVICES; TO PROVIDE FOR DISTRIBUTION OF FUNDS; TO REQUIRE THE BOARD OF TRUSTEES OF STATE INSTITUTIONS OF HIGHER LEARNING TO CONDUCT A BIENNIAL FACILITIES ASSESSMENT OF ALL PUBLIC HBCS AND DISBURSE MONIES ACCORDINGLY; TO PROVIDE FOR COMPETITIVE GRANTS; TO PROVIDE APPROPRIATE SOURCES OF MONIES FOR THE FUND; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
